PyLyrics is a python module to get Lyrics of songs from 
lyrics.wikia.com. It has support for getting albums of a singer and 
songs from an album from which lyrics can be accessed.

Note:
python3-beautifulsoup4 applied in orther to temporary solve issue with
BeautifulSoup4 slackbuild if you're on python3.10.
Although it's not recommended, you can install it dirty way with pip3
too.

By ~red
